<page RTP_instructions>
^^Well done. You will now continue to the next part of the experiment. 
^^IMPORTANT: In the next task, you will have to use what you just learned in order to figure out which words go together.
^^The following task is crucial for the experiment - please take your time and try to respond as ACCURATELY as possible.
^^We will no longer tell you when you are correct or incorrect. This part of the experiment is designed to test what you have just learned.
</page>

